body_html:
@npanpaliya - I think the test TwoDimensionalResize and ThreeDimensionalResize also need to change.

The issue is ThreeDimensionalResize and ThreeDimensionalResize8Bit were taking the same input and expecting different output. The test should take the same input and expect the same output. If changing the uint8 test input, you need to change the float32 test input.
